List of all members.

Detailed Description

Describes the initial view. Should be serialized before any drawables (if possible).

WHIP! data authors wishing to persist view other than the initial view should use the WT_Named_View object.

See also:
WT_Rendering_Options, WT_Named_View
Examples:

WhipExamples/View.cpp.

Warning:

Bug:
Not all objects perform skip_operand() correctly; this is a known problem. For best results, if client code must use WT_File::get_next_object_shell() manually, it should also call the corresponding WT_Object::materialize() method to avoid this problem.
